videos.description: Eric Paschall puts in a tough jumper at the end of the half but Villanoca trails La Salle at the break 42-39.
videos.headline: Paschall makes tough shot to shrink halftime deficit

videos.description: Miles Brookins grabs the pass and flushes a 2-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Le Salle' Brookins throws down dunk

videos.description: Saddiq Bey is fouled on a 3-pointer and the ensuing free throw gives Villanova a lead by 1 over La Salle.
videos.headline: Bey gives caps Nova comeback with 4-point play

videos.description: Nova's Phil Booth bum-rushes the rim for a nice slam.
videos.headline: Phil Booth slams home nice dunk

videos.description: Eric Paschall follows a missed shot with an emphatic putback slam.
videos.headline: Paschall putback slam extends Villanova's lead
